        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>pork mince </strong>(remove the paper if required!) and cook for 5-6 min or until browned and crisped, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
