    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>sticky chilli sauce</strong> and cook for 2 min or until everything is coated and sticky and the pork is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>sticky chilli pork stir-fry</strong></p>",
