      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sticky chilli pork stir-fry</strong> over the<strong> basmati rice</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over your <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
